flowchart TD
    A([User opens Login]) --> B[Choose Google/Microsoft SSO through Firebase]
    B --> C[Complete provider authentication]
    C --> D{Firebase token verified?}
    D -- No --> E[Show SSO unavailable or invalid]
    E --> F[Offer email/password login]
    D -- Yes --> G{Firebase UID maps exactly to one user?}
    G -- No --> H[Block login and show support guidance]
    G -- Yes --> I{Account active and IP allowed?}
    I -- No --> J[Show secure denial message]
    I -- Yes --> K{Password configured?}
    K -- No --> L[Create restricted setup session]
    L --> M[Redirect to password setup]
    M --> N[Create password]
    N --> O{Restricted MFA enrollment required?}
    O -- Yes --> P[Enroll and verify MFA]
    O -- No --> Q[Require fresh/full login]
    P --> Q
    K -- Yes --> R{MFA challenge required?}
    R -- Yes --> S[Complete MFA challenge]
    R -- No --> T[Create full session]
    S --> T
    Q --> A
    T --> U([Open HRMS dashboard])
